ialready peered with a few others on several of your nodes, but you		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ihaven't finished on your internal routing yet.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iSo you plan to configure OSPF. You opened Bird's configuration file		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iand added a protocol:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
